But maybe-maybe I don't want to be that.

832
00:39:45.842 --> 00:39:48.512
Or maybe I don't want to be that
all the time.

833
00:39:48.595 --> 00:39:51.973
Has it ever occurred to you
that. sometimes.

834
00:39:52.057 --> 00:39:54.017
I want to be the one
that's being taken care of?

835
00:39:54.101 --> 00:39:55.852
I would do that.

836
00:39:55.936 --> 00:39:58.396
Just tell me what you need.

837
00:40:00.690 --> 00:40:04.277
I want someone who knows what I need
without me having to say it.

838
00:40:04.361 --> 00:40:06.655
How am I supposed to do that?

839
00:40:09.741 --> 00:40:11.118
I don't know.

840
00:40:18.917 --> 00:40:21.545
If you came to apologize.
Percy's not here.

841
00:40:22.921 --> 00:40:24.798
I think I'm fucked up.

842
00:40:27.134 --> 00:40:30.137
Look. I shouldn't have said
what I said earlier.

843
00:40:30.762 --> 00:40:32.013
It's still true.

844
00:40:33.765 --> 00:40:36.560
No one would go to Charlie Florek
for a real relationship.

845
00:40:36.643 --> 00:40:41.106
Shit. Most of my life.
that's been a point of pride.

846
00:40:41.189 --> 00:40:42.899
But now?

847
00:40:42.983 --> 00:40:44.317
I don't know.

848
00:40:44.401 --> 00:40:47.946
Maybe it's my mom dying. or Sam proposing.

849
00:40:48.029 --> 00:40:50.407
Wait. Sam's proposing? To Taylor?

850
00:40:53.785 --> 00:40:56.454
Well. that explains
why Percy's been spiraling.

851
00:40:58.039 --> 00:41:01.209
But I don't want to be this forever.

852
00:41:03.211 --> 00:41:05.463
Maybe it's time to change.

853
00:41:06.548 --> 00:41:09.551
I know you're in the middle
