854
00:41:10.802 --> 00:41:13.555
But would you want to try? With me?

855
00:41:23.732 --> 00:41:25.317
Look. there have been times...

856
00:41:26.693 --> 00:41:31.990
Most of my life really.
where I would've jumped on that.

857
00:41:34.284 --> 00:41:37.537
But I feel like we both
have work to do. and...

858
00:41:39.456 --> 00:41:42.459
Just. I'm pretty sure
we need to do it on our own.

859
00:41:43.251 --> 00:41:44.419
I'm sorry.

860
00:42:03.021 --> 00:42:04.981
-Hey.
-Hey.

861
00:42:05.065 --> 00:42:07.234
