868
00:42:28.880 --> 00:42:32.300
Mint chip. That's my favorite.

869
00:42:32.384 --> 00:42:35.262
Yeah. I remembered.
Anyways. uh. you... I'll text you.

870
00:42:35.345 --> 00:42:37.347
